title: Couple With Heart Woman Person Medium Light Skin Tone
alsoKnownAs: Couple With Heart (Person, Man, Medium-Light Skin Tone, Medium-Dark Skin Tone)
description: Represents a romantic couple, specifically a person and a man, with their skin tones indicated as medium-light and medium-dark. Often used to express love, relationships, and partnerships.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, this charming emoji depicts a couple with a woman, rendered with a warm medium-light skin tone, embracing. A vibrant, soft red heart floats gently between them, embodying affection and connection with Apple's signature glossy 3D shading. The smooth gradients and realistic lighting on Apple devices highlight the tender bond, making it a perfect representation of love and partnership in digital conversations.
